communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

1. All of Oaklands contracts with Public Risk Innovation, Solutions and Management  made between January 1st 2018 to May 5th, 2023.

2. All of Oaklands contracts with C/O Alliant Insurance Services made between January 1st 2018 to May 5th, 2023.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Robbie Powelson

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

1. All contracts made between the City of Los Angeles and the Great American Insurance Company made between the years 2018 to 2023.

2. All contracts made between the City of Los Angeles and the Quality Comp Inc. made between the years 2018 to 2023.

3. All contracts made between the City of Los Angeles and the Great American Alliance Insurance Company made between the years 2018 to 2023.

4. All contracts made between the City of Los Angeles and Underwriters at Lloyds, London made between the years 2018 to 2023.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Robbie Powelson
